            <lg xml:id="TK952">
<l>oḻukkamum vāymaiyu nāṇumim mūṉṟu </l>
<l>miḻukkār kuṭippiṟan tār</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The high-born will never deviate from these three; good manners, truthfulness and modesty.</l>
